Yukon Quartz Mining Act
PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2002, No. 8, TR'O-JU-WECH'IN HERITAGE SITE, TR'ONDËK H'WËCH'IN FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits, until October 1, 2008, the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on lands which may be required for the settlement of Aboriginal land claims, and (b) repeals the Prohibition of Entry Order, made on October 1, 1998.
